      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## рҹҰ• Take the Tab\n\nSmall release, big quality-of-life: the alias autocomplete now listens to **Tab**.\n\n### вҢЁпёҸ Choose your accept key\n\nBoth accept keys have their own switch in the settings вҖ” mix and match:\n\n- **Accept suggestion with Enter** вҖ” the classic. Turn it off if you'd rather keep Enter for line breaks even while the popup is open.\n- **Accept suggestion with Tab** вҖ” the IDE feel. On by default.\n\nThe popup's footer hints adjust to whatever combination you pick, and Esc still dismisses without a trace. If you turn Enter acceptance off, pressing Enter with the popup open simply breaks the line вҖ” and a fully typed alias still links on its way out, exactly like before the popup existed.\n\nHappy linking. рҹҰ•\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/polygonhunter/linkosaurus/compare/3.5.1...3.6.0",
